snippet: The qualifier Filip Krajinovic defeated Fabio Fognini, the defending champion and the second seed, 6-4, 6-0, as a host of seeded players crashed out Wednesday in the second round of the Hamburg Open in Germany.
abstract: Filip Krajinovic defeats Fabio Fognini in second round of Hamburg Open tennis tournament; other tennis matches noted.
lead_paragraph: The qualifier Filip Krajinovic defeated Fabio Fognini, the defending champion and the second seed, 6-4, 6-0, as a host of seeded players crashed out Wednesday in the second round of the Hamburg Open in Germany.
